column2: select top # p.objid, p.petroMag_r, p.extinction_r, p.petroR5#_r, s.velDisp, s.z as redshift from PhotoObj as p join SpecObj as s on s.bestobjid = p.objid where (p.petroR9#_r / p.petroR5#_r) > #; (p.petroMag_g - p.extinction_g - p.petroMag_r + p.extinction_r) > #.; p.petroMag_r between # and #; s.z < #; s.zErr < power (#, #) ; s.velDisp > #; (s.velDispErr / s.velDisp) < #; p.petroMagErr_r < #;
